 sweep across the face, from the apples of your cheeks to your temples. Build to desired color intensity.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003emica, silica, cetearyl ethylhexanoate, zinc stearate, dimethicone, dodecane, rosa damascena flower oil, capsicum annuum extract, butyrospermum parkii (shea) butter, helianthus annuus (sunflower) seed oil, ethylhexylglycerin, tocopherol, glycerin, squalene, caprylic/capric triglyceride, c30-45 alkyl dimethicone, phenylisopropyl dimethicone, dimethiconol, diethylhexyl syringylidenemalonate, triethylhexanoin, cetyl peg/ppg-10/1 dimethicone, sucrose acetate isobutyrate, sorbitan sesquioleate, beta-sitosterol, xanthan gum, citric acid, sodium benzoate, sodium salicylate, citronellyl methylcrotonate, red 6 lake / ci 15850, red 7 lake / ci 15850, red 40 lake / ci 16035, yellow 5 lake / ci 19140, iron oxides / ci 77491, iron oxides / ci 77492, titanium dioxide / ci 77891.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"36:Tc89,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKN95 Face Mask 5 Layers Protection: Ultimate Defense Against Particulates\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eProduct Highlights:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eFive-Layer Filtration: Provides high-efficiency particle filtration for enhanced protection.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eIndividually Wrapped: Ensures hygiene and safety for each mask.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eComfortable Fit: Adjustable nose clip and soft material for prolonged wear.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eProduct Key Specifications Table:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\"\u003e\n\u003ctable\u003e\u003ccolgroup\u003e\u003ccol width=\"243\"\u003e\u003ccol width=\"381\"\u003e\u003c/colgroup\u003e\n\u003ctbody\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eSpecification\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eDetails\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eItem Form\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eMask\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eFeatures\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eFive-layer protection, Individually wrapped\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eSkin Type\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eSize\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eOne size fits most\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eCount\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eAvailable in multiple package counts\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eApplication\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003ePersonal protection against airborne particles\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eUsed for\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eDust, Pollen, Smoke protection\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eProduct Long Description:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eThe KN95 Face Mask offers 5 layers of high-efficiency protection to shield against various airborne particles, including dust, pollen, and smoke. This mask is designed for everyday use with comfort in mind; the adjustable nose clip ensures a snug and secure fit, while the soft material allows for prolonged wear without discomfort. Each mask is individually wrapped, promoting hygiene and safety. Ideal for use in public settings, the KN95 mask is a must-have for personal health defense.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eProduct Benefits:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eHigh-Efficiency Filtration: Targets and filters out small particles.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eEnhanced Comfort: Soft, breathable material for all-day wear.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eHygienic: Individually wrapped to maintain cleanliness and safety.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eHow to Use:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eWash hands before touching the mask.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eInspect the mask for any damages.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eAdjust the nose clip to fit snugly around the nose.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eEnsure the mask covers the mouth and nose completely.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eDispose of the mask properly after use.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eSafety Guide:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eDo not reuse disposable masks.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eIf the mask is damaged or soiled, replace it immediately.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eFor personal safety, avoid touching the mask while wearing it.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"37:T76f,\u003cp\u003eThe product is more likely to allow the skin to absorb, to achieve the role of the second skin cleansing, deep purification of the skin, add enough water.\u003cbr\u003eReduce the common water in the micro-organisms, pesticide residues on the skin hazards. After multiple water treatment of deionized water, deep purification of the skin, easier to absorb nutrients.\u003cbr\u003eBusy morning skin care only need to gently spray a spray, moisturizing water all day, before the makeup gently spray a spray, balance oil, make makeup fresh, dry season, gently spray a spray, so that the skin drink full water!\u003cbr\u003eAs long as you are willing, 75ml specifications can carry, convenient, lightweight, is your quick replenishment choice.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOil and water do mix, for twice the impact - just shake. A dual-phase, easy-does-it formula that sweeps off even tenacious waterproof mascara and lip colour. Absolutely gentle, suitable for all. Cucumber extract soothes and refreshes. Rinse with cool water.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRemoves waterproof makeup\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoothes skin\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDermatologist tested\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOphthalmologist tested\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-acnegenic\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan class=\"sku-ingredients js-sku-ingredients\"\u003eIngredients: \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"key-value\"\u003eAqua, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Isododecane, Hydro- Xyethyl Urea, Propylene Glycol, *Serine, Glycerin, Lauryl Glucoside, Sodium Chloride, Hydrolyzed Jojoba Esters, Phenoxyethanol, Cucumis Sativus Extract.\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan class=\"sku-ingredients-number js-sku-ingredients-number\"\u003eRecmmended Usage:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAfter cleansing, take an appropriate amount (approx. the size of a tiny coin) onto the palm and spread across the face.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePat lightly until it is fully absorbed into skin. (Cotton pad need not be used.)\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMade in PRC\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e38:Ta32,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eIntroducing the SKIN1004 Madagascar Centella Probio-Cica Bakuchiol Eye Cream, a powerful yet gentle solution for the delicate eye area. This 20ml (0.68 fl.oz) eye cream harnesses the potent benefits of centella asiatica, a plant renowned for its soothing and healing properties. Enriched with bakuchiol, a plant-based alternative to retinol, it helps diminish the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles while promoting a smoother, more youthful-looking complexion. The probiotics in this formula aid in strengthening the skin's natural barrier, while the cica (centella) extract soothes and calms irritation. Lightweight and easily absorbed, this eye cream hydrates and nourishes the sensitive eye area, leaving it refreshed and revitalised. Suitable for all skin types, including sensitive skin, this eye cream is a must-have for anyone seeking a comprehensive solution to target signs of ageing and fatigue around the eyes.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCentella-Infused Formula:\u003c/strong\u003e Enriched with centella asiatica extract, this eye cream helps soothe and calm sensitive skin around the delicate eye area.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBakuchiol Power: \u003c/strong\u003eFeaturing bakuchiol, a plant-based retinol alternative, this cream aims to diminish the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eProbiotic Complex:\u003c/strong\u003e Formulated with a probiotic complex, it aims to strengthen the skin's natural barrier and promote a healthy microbiome.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLightweight Texture:\u003c/strong\u003e With a lightweight, non-greasy texture, this eye cream absorbs quickly and leaves no residue.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHydrating Formula: \u003c/strong\u003eDesigned to deeply hydrate and nourish the under-eye area, leaving it smooth and supple.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\"\u003eMade in Korea\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"39:Ta22,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eElevate your makeup routine with the Tint Blush Pro 7ml, a versatile and long-lasting liquid blush that delivers a natural, radiant flush of colour. This ultra-blendable formula glides effortlessly onto the skin, blending seamlessly for a soft, diffused finish. The buildable pigmentation allows you to customise the intensity, from a subtle hint of colour to a bold, vibrant pop. The lightweight, non-drying formula is enriched with nourishing ingredients that leave your complexion looking fresh and luminous. Available in a range of flattering shades, this liquid blush is perfect for creating a healthy, radiant glow. Simply dab onto the apples of your cheeks and blend outward for a natural-looking flush that lasts all day.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVelvety Texture:\u003c/strong\u003e This tint blush features a smooth, velvety texture that blends seamlessly into the skin for a natural-looking flush of colour.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBuildable Pigmentation:\u003c/strong\u003e With its buildable formula, you can achieve a subtle wash of colour or build it up for a more intense, vibrant look.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLong-Lasting Wear: \u003c/strong\u003eThe long-wearing formula ensures your rosy glow stays put throughout the day without fading or creasing.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVersatile Shade:\u003c/strong\u003e The universally flattering pink shade complements a wide range of skin tones, making it a versatile addition to any makeup collection.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCompact Size: \u003c/strong\u003eHoused in a sleek, compact case, this blush is perfect for on-the-go touch-ups and travel.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsage:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eApply to the apples of the cheeks and blend outward.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"3a:Td4f,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eSwiss Beauty Matte Liquid Lipstick Cafe 03\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eDescription:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eIntroducing Swiss Beauty’s Ultra Smooth Matte Liquid Lipstick – the ultimate comfort-meets-performance product that is sure to take your lipstick game to the next level. This lightweight, long-wear lipstick is the perfect addition to any makeup kit, allowing you to enjoy a smooth, buttery-soft finish all day long.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eThis transferproof formula is designed to glide on effortlessly in a single swipe, without smudging, bleeding, or flaking. The breathable film technology ensures that your lips are comfortable, even during extended wear. The non-sticky formulation is packed with intense pigments that don’t feather or dry out your lips, providing a head-turning effect that’s sure to make you stand out in a crowd.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eWhether you’re looking for a bold pop of colour or a more subtle, natural finish, Swiss Beauty’s Ultra Smooth Matte Liquid Lipstick has got you covered. Available in a range of shades to suit all skin tones, this high-performing lipstick is perfect for those who want fuller, high-shine dazzling lips without any compromise.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eWith its long-lasting wear and comfortable feel, Swiss Beauty’s Ultra Smooth Matte Liquid Lipstick is the perfect choice for any occasion. So why wait? Treat yourself to a lipstick that feels like second-skin and experience the ultimate in comfort, performance, and style.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eSmooth Matte Finish: This lightweight, long-wear lipstick glides on effortlessly and delivers a smooth, matte finish that looks and feels amazing.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eIntense, long-lasting colour: The high-performing formula is packed with intense pigments that deliver head-turning colour that lasts all day without smudging or bleeding.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eComfortable and breathable: The breathable film technology ensures that your lips feel comfortable even during extended wear, making it perfect for all-day use.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eNon-sticky and non-drying: The non-sticky, non-drying formulation provides a comfortable wear and prevents feathering, flaking or drying of lips.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eVersatile shade range: Available in a range of shades, this lipstick is perfect for all skin tones and can be used to create a variety of different looks, from bold to natural.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"3c:T822,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eNatura Glow Shampoo + Conditioner Hair Fall Control \u0026amp; Hair Beauty (200ml) is a dual-action hair care product formulated to reduce hair fall while enhancing hair’s overall beauty and manageability. This shampoo and conditioner combination gently cleanses the scalp and hair, providing essential nutrients to improve strength and reduce breakage, resulting in visibly healthier and shinier hair.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Features:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHair Fall Control:\u003c/strong\u003e Specially formulated to target hair fall, strengthening hair from root to tip and reducing hair breakage.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e2-in-1 Shampoo and Conditioner: \u003c/strong\u003eCombines the benefits of a shampoo and conditioner for simplified hair care, offering both cleansing and conditioning in one product.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eImproved Hair Texture: \u003c/strong\u003eEnhances hair softness, making it more manageable and smooth, while promoting a radiant shine.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNourishing Formula\u003c/strong\u003e: Enriched with ingredients that nourish the scalp, support hair health, and add vibrancy.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eNatura Glow Shampoo + Conditioner is ideal for individuals looking to simplify their routine without compromising on hair health. This product not only helps reduce hair fall but also works to enhance hair’s natural beauty, making it suitable for regular use across hair types, especially for those experiencing weak or brittle hair.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"3d:T529,\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNatura Clear \u0026amp; Glow Complete Care Facewash (100ml)\u003c/strong\u003e is specially designed to cleanse, brighten, and rejuvenate the skin. Formulated with gentle yet effective ingredients, this facewash removes impurities while helping to maintain a natural glow, making it suitable for daily use on all skin types.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eKey Features:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBrightening Formula\u003c/strong\u003e: Helps promote a clear and glowing complexion by removing dirt, oil, and impurities.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGentle Cleansing\u003c/strong\u003e: Thoroughly cleanses the skin without causing dryness, preserving natural moisture.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSuitable for All Skin Types\u003c/strong\u003e: Safe for regular use, even on sensitive skin.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRefreshing Scent\u003c/strong\u003e: Leaves a light, refreshing fragrance that uplifts the senses during use.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eBenefits:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eNatura Clear \u0026amp; Glow Facewash supports clean, radiant skin and is ideal for anyone looking to achieve a refreshed, glowing complexion with consistent daily use.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e3e:T7f2,\u003cp\u003eNatura Expert Care Body Lotion is a rich, skin-softening moisturizer formulated to repair, hydrate, and protect dry or rough skin. Enriched with Shea Butter, Cocoa Butter, and Coconut Milk, it penetrates deeply to restore moisture and improve skin texture. Its non-greasy, fast-absorbing formula makes it ideal for daily use, leaving your skin feeling smooth, supple, and radiant.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShea Butter\u003c/strong\u003e: Heals and softens skin throughout the year.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCocoa Butter\u003c/strong\u003e: Repairs and moisturizes dry areas.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCoconut Milk\u003c/strong\u003e: Deeply nourishes and enhances skin softness.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFast-Absorbing Texture\u003c/st"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"rong\u003e: Non-greasy and lightweight.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSuitable for All Skin Types\u003c/strong\u003e: Gentle enough for sensitive skin.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMade in Bangladesh\u003c/strong\u003e: Locally crafted with high-quality ingredients.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProvides deep hydration and long-lasting moisture.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHelps repair and restore dry, flaky, or rough skin.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eImproves skin elasticity and smoothness.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLeaves skin feeling soft, healthy, and glowing.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIdeal for daily use, especially in dry or cold climates.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e Usage Instructions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTake a generous amount of lotion in your palms.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eApply evenly to clean, dry skin.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMassage gently in circular motions until fully absorbed.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFocus on dry areas like elbows, knees, and heels.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse twice daily for best results.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e Why Choose Natura Expert Care Body Lotion?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCombines natural moisturizers with expert-level skin care.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOffers visible results in hydration and skin texture.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTrusted by users for its quality, affordability, and effectiveness.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA great choice for those seeking gentle yet powerful nourishment.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRanked among the best-selling body lotions in its category.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c/p\u003e3f:T4ea,\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eTired of rough, frizzy, and damaged hair? Try Natura Repair Shampoo + Conditioner. Enriched with Jojoba Oil and Shea Butter, and boosted with Vitamin B3, B5 \u0026amp; Keratin.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eJojoba Oil: \u003c/strong\u003eMoisturizes and repairs dry, brittle hair and adds natural shine\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShea Butter: \u003c/strong\u003eDeeply nourishes and softens hair, repairing dryness and breakage \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVitamin B3: \u003c/strong\u003eImproves scalp circulation and promotes healthier hair growth\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVitamin B5:\u003c/strong\u003e Strengthens hair strands and locks in long-lasting hydration\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKeratin:\u003c/strong\u003e Rebuilds damaged hair structure, adding strength, shine, and smoothness\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e40:T8a8,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003eNatura Grow Shampoo + Conditioner is a 2-in-1 hair care solution enriched with the natural goodness of Ginger Oil, Onion Oil, Aloe Vera, and Milk Protein. This powerful blend is crafted to reduce hair fall, strengthen strands, and boost volume while gently cleansing and conditioning your hair. Ideal for both men and women, it’s a daily essential for healthier, shinier, and more resilient hair.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e Key Features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGinger Oil \u0026amp; Onion Oil\u003c/strong\u003e: Stimulate the scalp and reduce hair fall.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAloe Vera\u003c/strong\u003e: Soothes the scalp and hydrates hair.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMilk Protein\u003c/strong\u003e: Strengthens and repairs damaged strands.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e2-in-1 Formula\u003c/strong\u003e: Combines shampoo and conditioner for convenience.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSulfate-Free\u003c/strong\u003e: Gentle on all hair types, including color-treated hair.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMade in Bangladesh\u003c/strong\u003e: Locally crafted with trusted ingredients.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eReduces hair fall\u003c/strong\u003e visibly within 3 weeks of regular use.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBoosts volume\u003c/strong\u003e for a fuller, thicker appearance.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStrengthens strands\u003c/strong\u003e, minimizing breakage and split ends.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eImproves manageability\u003c/strong\u003e, making hair easier to style.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAdds shine and softness\u003c/strong\u003e, leaving hair looking healthy and vibrant.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSafe for daily use\u003c/strong\u003e, even on sensitive scalps.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eUsage Instructions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWet hair thoroughly.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eApply a generous amount to the scalp and massage gently.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork the lather through to the ends of your hair.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRinse thoroughly with clean water.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse regularly for best results.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy Choose Natura Grow Shampoo + Conditioner?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCombines natural ingredients with proven hair care science.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOffers visible results in volume, strength, and shine.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSaves time with its 2-in-1 convenience.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTrusted by users for its gentle formula and effectiveness.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA top choice for those seeking affordable, salon-quality care at home\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"41:T567,\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNatura Glow Hair Oil (100ml)\u003c/strong\u003e is a specially formulated oil designed to nourish, protect, and enhance the natural beauty of your hair. This hair oil combines the benefits of natural ingredients that work together to improve hair health, manageability, and shine.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eKey Features:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNourishing Formula\u003c/strong\u003e: Enriched with a blend of oils that deeply penetrate the hair shaft to provide essential nutrients, promoting stronger and healthier hair.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRestores Shine\u003c/strong\u003e: Helps restore the natural luster of hair, making it look vibrant and well-maintained.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eImproves Manageability\u003c/strong\u003e: Softens hair, reducing frizz and tangles, making it easier to style.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSupports Scalp Health\u003c/strong\u003e: The nourishing properties of the oil can help soothe the scalp and prevent dryness, promoting overall hair growth.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eBenefits:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNatura Glow Hair Oil is ideal for all hair types, especially for those looking to restore moisture and shine. Regular use can lead to visibly healthier hair, making it a must-have in your hair care routine. This product is perfect for those who desire strong, shiny, and manageable hair without the use of harsh chemicals.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor further details, consider checking specific beauty or personal care product reviews and descriptions online.\u003c/p\u003e42:T8e6,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003eNatura Clear \u0026amp; Glow Face Wash is an all-weather, all-skin-type cleanser designed to tackle common skin concerns like acne, tanning, dullness, and uneven tone. Enriched with Neem Extract, Rice Powder, Honey, and Saffron, it gently removes impurities while nourishing and revitalizing your skin. Whether you're stepping out or winding down, this face wash is your daily glow-up companion.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNeem Extract\u003c/strong\u003e: Natural antiseptic that helps prevent breakouts and purifies skin.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRice Powder\u003c/strong\u003e: Reduces tanning and sun damage, restoring your natural complexion.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHoney \u0026amp; Saffron\u003c/strong\u003e: Soften, brighten, and add a radiant glow.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGentle Formula\u003c/strong\u003e: Cleanses without stripping moisture.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDay \u0026amp; Night Use\u003c/strong\u003e: Ideal for morning refresh and nighttime detox.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMade in Bangladesh\u003c/strong\u003e: Locally crafted with trusted ingredients.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFights pimples and acne with antibacterial action.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReduces tanning and pigmentation for a more even skin tone.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLeaves skin feeling soft, smooth, and glowing.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHydrates and soothes with anti-inflammatory properties.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDermatologist-tested and safe for all skin types, including sensitive skin.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnriched with Vitamin C and Rosehip Extract to reduce blemishes and hydrate dry skin.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsage Instructions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e Splash water on your face.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTake a small amount of face wash.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e Massage gently in circular motions.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRinse thoroughly with clean water.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePat dry and follow with moisturizer.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse twice daily—morning and night—for best results.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e Why Choose Natura Clear \u0026amp; Glow Face Wash?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCombines natural ingredients with modern skincare science.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOffers multi-action care: cleansing, brightening, anti-acne, and anti-tan.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTrusted by users for its gentle yet effective formula.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA budget-friendly way to achieve radiant, healthy skin.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePerfect for those seeking a complete care solution in one bottle.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"44:T9fe,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp class=\"\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDetails:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eSHEGLAM\u0026nbsp;MATTE\u0026nbsp;ALLURE\u0026nbsp;Liquid\u0026nbsp;Lipstick\u0026nbsp;delivers\u0026nbsp;you\u0026nbsp;highly-saturated\u0026nbsp;matte\u0026nbsp;finish\u0026nbsp;with\u0026nbsp;lightweight\u0026nbsp;no-drying\u0026nbsp;feeling\u0026nbsp;and\u0026nbsp;long-lasting\u0026nbsp;wearability\u0026nbsp;over\u0026nbsp;hours.\u0026nbsp;This\u0026nbsp;liquid\u0026nbsp;lipstick\u0026nbsp;has\u0026nbsp;high\u0026nbsp;intensity\u0026nbsp;pigment\u0026nbsp;and\u0026nbsp;moisturizing\u0026nbsp;ingredients,\u0026nbsp;which\u0026nbsp;gi