 12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Please\u0026nbsp;note:\u0026nbsp;Before\u0026nbsp;using\u0026nbsp;this\u0026nbsp;product,\u0026nbsp;please\u0026nbsp;read\u0026nbsp;the\u0026nbsp;ingredient\u0026nbsp;list\u0026nbsp;carefully\u0026nbsp;to\u0026nbsp;ensure\u0026nbsp;that\u0026nbsp;they\u0026nbsp;are\u0026nbsp;suitable\u0026nbsp;for\u0026nbsp;your\u0026nbsp;personal\u0026nbsp;use. ISODODECANE, NYLON-12, ISONONYL ISONONANOATE, ACRYLATES COPOLYMER, ISOHEXADECANE, HYDROGENATED STYRENE/ISOPRENE COPOLYMER, QUATERNIUM-18 HECTORITE, PHENOXYETHANOL, CAPRYLYL GLYCOL, TOCOPHERYL ACETATE, TITANIUM DIOXIDE (CI 77891), IRON OXIDES(CI 77491), IRON OXIDES (CI 77492, IRON OXIDES(CI 77499, YELLOW 5 LAKE(CI 19140), RED 7 LAKE (CI 15850).\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"45:T5ea,\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003eThe St. Ives Purifying Tea Tree \u0026amp; Lemongrass Body Wash is a purifying body cleanser that removes excess oil without drying and delivers a clean you can feel. This paraben-free, dermatologist tested formula removes dirt and oil and leaves skin feeling fresh, clean and smelling great. The St. Ives Purifying Tea Tree \u0026amp; Lemongrass Body Wash is made with 100% natural tea tree and lemongrass extracts, plant-based cleansers and contains no animal-derived ingredients. A shower gel that was designed to deliver a deep clean. All that in a 100% recycled bottle.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e HOW TO USE:\u003c/strong\u003e It's as simple as: pour, later, rinse. That's all there is to it, now it's time to enjoy a moment to yourself. St. Ives: get to know us. At St. Ives, we use 100% naturally sourced moisturizers, exfoliants, and extracts to bring the joy of nature into our cruelty-free skin products to give you soft, refreshed skin that glows. And we mean it, too. That\u0026rsquo;s why we celebrate the look and feel of real, natural skin, and none of the models on our site have been retouched to hide any of their features that make them unique. Are you excited? Good. Now let's get your glow on!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"\u003eMade in USA\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e46:T6fc,\u003cp\u003eThis brightening cream cleanser deeply cleanses, hydrates, and brightens, for a more even \u0026amp; glowing skin. Gently removes make-up \u0026amp; impurities, while maintaining skin's natural moisture barrier. Enriched with [VITAMIN C**]known as a dermatological active that brightens, boost glow, and enhance skin's radiance \u0026amp; [GLYCERIN] known as a humectant from its natural origin to deeply hydrates and protects skin barrier Gentle Formula: Its microbiome friendly \u0026amp; sulfate free* formula is pH neutral to the s"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"kin and dermatologically tested.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e2050734 7 - INGREDIENTS:\u0026nbsp;\u003cspan data-iopelement=\"AQUA / WATER\"\u003eAQUA / WATER\u003c/span\u003e,\u0026nbsp;\u003cspan data-iopelement=\"GLYCERIN\"\u003eGLYCERIN\u003c/span\u003e, COCAMIDOPROPYL BETAINE. SODIUM C14-16 OLEFIN SULFONATE. GLYCOL DISTEARATE,\u0026nbsp;\u003cspan data-iopelement=\"TRIETHYL CITRATE\"\u003eTRIETHYL CITRATE\u003c/span\u003e,\u0026nbsp;\u003cspan data-iopelement=\"PEG-55 PROPYLENE GLYCOL OLEATE\"\u003ePEG-55 PROPYLENE GLYCOL OLEATE\u003c/span\u003e,\u0026nbsp;\u003cspan data-iopelement=\"SODIUM CHLORIDE\"\u003eSODIUM CHLORIDE\u003c/span\u003e, SODIUM HYDROXIDE. COCO-BETAINE. ASCORBYL GLUCOSIDE,\u0026nbsp;\u003cspan data-iopelement=\"PROPYLENE GLYCOL\"\u003ePROPYLENE GLYCOL\u003c/span\u003e,\u0026nbsp;\u003cspan data-iopelement=\"CITRIC ACID\"\u003eCITRIC ACID\u003c/span\u003e,\u0026nbsp;\u003cspan data-iopelement=\"ACRYLATES COPOLYMER\"\u003eACRYLATES COPOLYMER\u003c/span\u003e,\u0026nbsp;\u003cspan data-iopelement=\"SODIUM BENZOATE\"\u003eSODIUM BENZOATE\u003c/span\u003e,\u0026nbsp;\u003cspan data-iopelement=\"BENZOIC ACID\"\u003eBENZOIC ACID\u003c/span\u003e,\u0026nbsp;\u003cspan data-iopelement=\"LINALOOL\"\u003eLINALOOL\u003c/span\u003e,\u0026nbsp;\u003cspan data-iopelement=\"LIMONENE\"\u003eLIMONENE\u003c/span\u003e,\u0026nbsp;\u003cspan data-iopelement=\"PARFUM / FRAGRANCE\"\u003ePARFUM / FRAGRANCE\u003c/span\u003e, (FIL. Z70034188/1).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eApply twice a day. Gently massage on wet skin. Rinse off. Avoid eye area. In case of contact with eyes rinse immediately.\u003c/p\u003e47:T68d,\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"\u003eEuzonea by Maison Alhambra is a feminine fragrance from the fruity floral family.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"\u003eEuzonea is a compelling fragrance that enchants the senses with its unique composition of precious notes. The Top Notes, with Pomegranate, Persimmon and Green Accords, create a fresh and fruity opening, inviting you on a vibrant olfactory journey from the first spray. In the heart, Orchid, Lotus and Champaca blend in a floral symphony, adding a note of elegance and sensuality.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"\u003eThe Base Notes of Mahogany, Amber, Violet and Whipped Cream give depth and envelopingness to Euzonea, leaving a lasting and unforgettable impression. This fragrance is ideal for those "])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"seeking a touch of luxury and refinement at all times.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 12p