lla that takes away the irritating latex smell and helps to give you a natural aroma to enjoy the union. As lack of lubrication is the third highest cause of condom splitting, the extra dash of flavoured lube in our condoms makes it extra safe, along with making the 'action' friction free and comfortable for both you and your partner, truly the best bubblegum flavoured condoms.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\"\u003eMEETS STRINGENT TESTING STANDARDS - All skins condoms carry the EU's highest standard CE mark, and are manufactured to ISO 4074 - the highest and most up to date of safety testing standards. This makes our extra safe condoms super safe, meeting the most strict and stringest of the testing criteria of all Europe.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\"\u003eTRUSTED \u0026amp; RECOMMENDED BY INDUSTRY EXPERTS - SKIN's Superior Quality \u0026amp; Standards along with strong ethos and value system, has earned us a name. Now backed by over 20 YEARS of experience, SKINS is one of the most credible voices that promote better sexual health and our products are widely RECOMMENDED BY EXPERTS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"provenanceCertifications_feature_div\" class=\"celwidget\" data-feature-name=\"provenanceCertifications\" data-csa-c-type=\"widget\" data-csa-c-content-id=\"provenanceCertifications\" data-csa-c-slot-id=\"provenanceCertifications_feature_div\" data-csa-c-asin=\"B00C3DOT72\" data-csa-c-is-in-initial-active-row=\"false\" data-csa-c-id=\"6ss99m-lbd5p1-jbtg6b-5yhdc7\" data-cel-widget=\"provenanceCertifications_feature_div\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"handmadeArtisanCard_feature_div\" class=\"celwidget\" data-feature-name=\"handmadeArtisanCard\" data-csa-c-type=\"widget\" data-csa-c-content-id=\"handmadeArtisanCard\" data-csa-c-slot-id=\"h