v class=\"a-row\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"a-section buying\"\u003e\n\u003ctable class=\"a-normal\"\u003e\n\u003ctbody\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd class=\"warningAlertImageColumn\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNot for sale to persons under the age of 18. By placing an order for this product, you declare that you are 18 years of age or over. This item must be used responsibly and appropriately.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eFrom the manufacturer\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"aplus-v2 desktop celwidget\" data-csa-c-id=\"dbw7al-ncz1h7-r3gs96-kx3rib\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"celwidget aplus-module module-12 aplus-standard\" data-csa-c-id=\"o4to1z-3hs1jz-kvqpct-c58izr\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-module-12\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"aplus-module-wrapper apm-spacing apm-floatnone apm-fixed-width\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"apm-sidemodule aplus-module-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"apm-hero-image\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/mg/3bc361f2-49d7-4621-86ca-4119ebd13952._SR970,300_.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/mg/3bc361f2-49d7-4621-86ca-4119ebd13952._SR970,300_.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"celwidget aplus-module module-3 aplus-standard\" data-csa-c-id=\"l1k8d2-o4m44t-r74y65-g0z9cq\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-module-3\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"aplus-module-wrapper apm-floatnone apm-fixed-width\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"apm-sidemodule apm-spacing\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"apm-sidemodule-imageright\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"a-spacing-mini\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/d6065f86-a685-49ea-8d88-0e12cc0dc2db._CR0,0,300,300_PT0_SX300__.jpg\" alt=\"Skins Condoms\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/d6065f86-a685-49ea-8d88-0e12cc0dc2db._CR0,0,300,300_PT0_SX300__.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"apm-sidemodule-textleft\"\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003eSkins\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhen it\u0026rsquo;s safe, having sex can be fun and beneficial to your health. Skins have carefully designed a range that aims to improve, satisfy and protect you during sex.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe trick is to find a condom that offers not only reassurance but also the best sensation possible. Instead of condoms ruining the moment Skins allow us to further enjoy sex and remind us that now, more than ever, they are essential wear.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026lsquo;Never Go In Without A Skin\u0026rsquo; is printed on every condom, making Skins the only condom brand that promotes a safe sex message on the foil. Skins also work in association with the NHS--so you can really let go and know you are in safe hands with a Skins condom.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"celwidget aplus-module module-10 aplus-standard\" data-csa-c-id=\"esjbh8-56o2f2-z3a9fw-hm62c8\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-module-10\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"aplus-module-wrapper apm-fixed-width\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"apm-spacing\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"apm-lefthalfcol\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cimg class=\"apm-floatleft a-spacing-mini\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/mg/e5ce2a75-8226-4d17-91ac-0dc894faae86._SL100__.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/mg/e5ce2a75-8226-4d17-91ac-0dc894faae86._SL100__.jpg\"\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"a-spacing-mini apm-iconheader\"\u003eNatural Feeling\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"a-spacing-base\"\u003eSkins look to source the very best ingredients to ensure a natural experience. They are 0.05m thinner than most other condom brands, this assures a comfortable Skin on Skin experience without compromising safety.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"apm-righthalfcol\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cimg class=\"apm-floatleft a-spacing-mini\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/mg/3553a327-7f4f-475c-964f-559afffccaa7._SL100__.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/mg/3553a327-7f4f-475c-964f-559afffccaa7._SL100__.jpg\"\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"a-spacing-mini apm-iconheader\"\u003eClear Condoms\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"a-spacing-base\"\u003eThe high quality latex used to make Skins condoms not only make them beautifully clear but also allows a man to look his very best when it matters most. It\u0026rsquo;s like putting on your favourite shirt; it enhances your best bits and makes you feel like you can take on the world. We encourage you to open them, compare with other condom brands and understand the difference for yourself. We call it INVISITEX (invisible latex) for a reason.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"apm-lefthalfcol\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cimg class=\"apm-floatleft a-spacing-mini\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/mg/a24497c1-3631-4509-a74d-1d562eff5760._SL100__.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/mg/a24497c1-3631-4509-a74d-1d562eff5760._SL100__.jpg\"\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"a-spacing-mini apm-iconheader\"\u003eNo Latex Smell\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"a-spacing-base\"\u003eAll Skins condoms are infused with a slight vanilla scent, so there is none of that tell tale smell that is sometimes associated with condoms. We\u0026rsquo;ve ensure