product off after use\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\"\u003eWORKS WITH LATEX CONDOMS: This delay spray for men is compatible with latex and polyisoprene condoms or can be used alone to help reduce sensitivity and prolong pleasure\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"a-list-item\"\u003eSAFE, HEALTHY, FUN: Trusted for over 100 years, Trojan promotes a safe, healthy, and fun sex life and is dedicated to delivering innovative, high-quality products that offer pleasure and protection\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"a-spacing-mini\"\u003e\n\u003ch2 class=\"default\"\u003eProduct Description\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"a-section a-spacing-small\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLast longer, prolong pleasure, and improve your “bed cred.” It’s all possible with Trojan Extended Pleasure Delay Spray. This spray is designed to enhance duration by desensitizing the male genital area and help prevent premature ejaculation. This easy-to-use endurance enhancer helps you last longer and keep the pleasure going. To use, spray a small amount directly to the head and shaft of your penis before intercourse, wait until it dries, and you’re ready to enjoy. Wash product off after use. The active ingredient in this 2.0 fl oz bottle of Trojan Extended Pleasure Delay Spray is Benzocaine 7.5%—a male genital desensitizer that helps reduce sensitivity and overstimulation. This desensitizing spray is compatible with latex and polyisoprene condoms. The Trojan Brand promotes a safe, healthy, and fun sex life. From condoms to vibrators to lubricants, the Trojan Brand is dedicated to delivering innovative, high-quality products that offer pleasure and protection.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"5e:T630,\u003cp\u003eMeet Manforce King Thin, the newest roya