6nbsp;latex,\u0026nbsp;it\u0026nbsp;is\u0026nbsp;non-toxic\u0026nbsp;and\u0026nbsp;safe.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSilky\u0026nbsp;smooth\u0026nbsp;premium\u0026nbsp;lubricated\u0026nbsp;for\u0026nbsp;comfort\u0026nbsp;and\u0026nbsp;sensitivity.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEasy\u0026nbsp;on\u0026nbsp;shape\u0026nbsp;makes\u0026nbsp;condom"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"s\u0026nbsp;easier\u0026nbsp;to\u0026nbsp;put\u0026nbsp;on\u0026nbsp;and\u0026nbsp;more\u0026nbsp;comfortable\u0026nbsp;to\u0026nbsp;wear.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe\u0026nbsp;special\u0026nbsp;reservoir\u0026nbsp;tip\u0026nbsp;provides\u0026nbsp;extra\u0026nbsp;safety\u0026nbsp;and\u0026nbsp;the\u0026nbsp;tapered\u0026nbsp;base\u0026nbsp;ensures\u0026nbsp;a\u0026nbsp;secure\u0026nbsp;fit.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSpecial\u0026nbsp;ultra\u0026nbsp;thin\u0026nbsp;design\u0026nbsp;bring\u0026nbsp;you\u0026nbsp;real\u0026nbsp;feel\u0026nbsp;experience.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTRANSPARENT: They are lubricated, durable, flexible, nearly see-through and built to last.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDISCREET SHIPMENT: No product name or brand name is mentioned on the package box, 100% privacy guaranteed.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e60:Tc3a,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eGreen Seven Sleep Balm is a soothing herbal remedy inspired by traditional Thai massage therapy. Crafted with a blend of natural ingredients, including lavender and other medicinal plant extracts, this balm is designed to promote relaxation, ease physical discomfort, and support restful sleep. Its compact 50g size makes it a convenient companion for daily wellness routines or travel.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eInfused with lavender and moisturizing herbs\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eBased on traditional Thai massage balm formulation\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eMade from natural ingredients including essential oils and herbal extracts\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eSmooth texture for easy application\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eCompact 50g packaging ideal for portability\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsage Instructions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eApply a small amount to temples, chest, or affected areas\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eMassage gently until absorbed\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eUse before bedtime to promote restful sleep\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eCan be used during massage therapy or as a daily calming aid\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eSuitable for external use only\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy Choose This Product\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eGreen Seven Sleep Balm offers a holistic approach to relaxation and wellness. Its natural formula is free from harsh chemicals and designed to deliver therapeutic benefits through aromatherapy and topical relief. Whether you're dealing with stress, muscle tension, or sleeplessness, this balm provides a gentle and effective solution rooted in traditional practices.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eImproves blood circulation\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eEnhances relaxation and stress relief\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eSoothes insect bites and minor skin irritations\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eEases muscle aches and joint discomfort\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eHelps relieve cold symptoms and nasal congestion\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eSupports deeper, more restful sleep\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCautions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eFor external use only\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eAvoid contact with eyes and mucous membranes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eKeep out of reach of children\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eDiscontinue use if irritation occurs\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eStore in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"61:Tb39,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;