=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003ePack size: 7g per balm, 8 units included.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eEasy to carry and apply.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eTraditional Thai formulation for effective relief.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c/strong\u003e Menthol 22.8% w/w, Camphor 22.8% w/w, Eucalyptus Oil 11.44% w/w\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsage Instructions:\u003c/strong\u003e Apply gently on temples, chest, or affected area for headaches, congestion, or insect bites. For dizziness or motion sickness, inhale directly from the balm. Store below 30°C.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCautions:\u003c/strong\u003e For external use only. Do not ingest, apply to lips, eyes, or open wounds. Not suitable for children under 3 years.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eIZE Jelli Balm II is a compact, effective, and multi-purpose solution for fast relief from common travel and daily discomforts.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"62:T9b8,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eThe \u003cstrong\u003eHong Thai Herbal Inhaler\u003c/strong\u003e, now conveniently available at \u003cstrong\u003eArogga\u003c/strong\