edients:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eMenthol: 20g\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eCamphor: 20g\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eBorneol: 15g\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eEucalyptus Oil: 5g\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eOther traditional herbs\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCountry of Origin:\u003c/strong\u003e Thailand\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"63:Taf9,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eThe Hong Thai Menthol Aromatherapy Nasal Inhaler is a convenient, double-sided inhaler designed to offer quick relief from nasal congestion and help you breathe easier anytime, anywhere. Whether you're feeling dizzy, nauseous, or simply need to refresh your senses, this aromatic solution is your on-the-go remedy. Keep it in your bag, at your desk, or bedside for an instant boost of clarity.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Benefits:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTemporarily relieves nasal congestion:\u003c/strong\u003e The strong menthol and eucalyptus aroma helps clear blocked sinuses and eases breathing.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eInstant aromatic refreshment:\u003c/strong\u003e One side is for direct inhalation, delivering a powerful scent that refreshes and awakens your senses.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDual-purpose design:\u003c/strong\u003e The other side contains a balm for external application, ideal for rubbing on temples or under the nose to soothe discomfort.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMultipurpose use:\u003c/strong\u003e Useful for cold symptoms, dizziness, nausea, and even avoiding unpleasant odors.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCompact and travel-friendly:\u003c/strong\u003e Comes in a handy size with 6 pieces per pack — perfect for travel, work, or everyday use.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsage:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003eInhale directly from the aromatic end to relieve nasal stuffiness or gain a quick mental refresh. Apply the balm end externally to areas like your temples or chest for soothing effects. Use as needed.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u0