;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"word\"\u003emin\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"word\"\u003eON/30\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"word\"\u003emin\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"word\"\u003eOFF\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBrand\u0026nbsp;\u003ca\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMicrolife\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eModel NEB 200\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOrigin Switzerland\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eProduct Description\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch1 class=\"a-size-large a-spacing-none\"\u003e\u003ca\u003eMicrolife NEB 200 Compressor Nebulizer\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Microlife NEB 200 Active is a daily, family-friendly compressor nebulizer. It is conveniently small, allowing easy transport and storage without taking up too much space\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMicrolife NEB 200 Compressor Inhaler Inhaler with Mouthpiece and Mask for Baby\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"grid__item one-third ipadp--one-whole two-list-right\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"text-align-center\"\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEfficient treatment\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor the upper and lower respiratory tract.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFast treatment\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHigh-speed nebulizer for short inhalation times.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEasy one-button operation\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuitable for the whole family.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNebulisation rate: 0.4 ml/min. (NaCI 0.9%)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eParticle size: 63% \u0026lt; 5 \u0026mu;m\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e2.83 \u0026mu;m (MMAD)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMax. free air flow: 15 l/min.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOperating airflow: 5.31 l/min.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAcoustic noise level: 52 dBA\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePower source: 230V 50 Hz AC\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePower lead length: 1.6 m\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNebulizer capacity: min. 2 ml; max. 8 ml\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eResidual volume: 0.8 ml\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-35919\" title=\"Microlife NEB 200 Compressor Nebulizer 1\" src=\"https://cdn2.arogga.com/eyJidWNrZXQiOiJhcm9nZ2EiLCJrZXkiOiJtZWRpY2luZURlc2NyaXB0aW9uXC8yOVwvMjk2MDgtMGxtemM0MWwwdzhhZiIsImVkaXRzIjpbXX0=\" alt=\"Microlife Nebulizer Compressor\" width=\"910\" height=\"875\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCompact \u0026amp; convenient\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eReliable piston pump\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFast and efficient treatment\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor the whole family\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSupplied with adult \u0026amp; child mouthpiece, nose piece, 5 pcs. of spare filters, and carrying bag\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEfficient Treatment \u0026ndash; For the upper and lower respiratory tract.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFast Treatment \u0026ndash; High-speed nebulizer for short inhalation times.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEasy One Button Operation \u0026ndash; Suitable for the whole family.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFully equipped with adult and child face, mouth and nosepiece, air hose, 5 replacement air filters, and carrying bag.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSafe and hygienic accessories are washable and disinfectable.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for all common inhalation solutions\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"66:T639,\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDescription:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eProvide effective respiratory treatment for your child with our Surgical Kit Nebulizer Mask. Designed specifically for children, this mask ensures efficient delivery of asthma medication to the lungs.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEfficient Nebulization:\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026nbsp;The mouthpiece design allows for targeted medication delivery, maximizing treatment effectiveness.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSuitable for All Ages:\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Ideal for children of all ages, including those below three years who may have difficulty using a facemask.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eComfortable Fit:\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Made from medical-grade, non-toxic PVC, the mask is flexible and transparent, providing a comfortable fit for your child.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEasy Cleaning:\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026nbsp;The mask can be easily cleaned by washing in warm, soapy water or soaking in a solution of white vinegar and water.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAdditional Information:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAvailable at reputable medical suppliers such as Docuses Healthcare and Arogga.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eConsult your healthcare provider for guidance on the best nebulizer mask for your child's specific needs.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTips for Using a Nebulizer with a Child:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHave your child sit upright during treatment.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProvide a calming activity to help them remain still.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe nebulizer will typically complete treatment within 10-15 minutes, indicated by a sputtering sound.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnsure your child keeps the mask on throughout the entire treatment duration.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e67:Td13,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eThe Omron NE-C101 Compressor Nebulizer is a user-friendly respiratory device designed to deliver fast and effective relief from asthma, bronchitis, COPD, and other respiratory conditions. Engineered for both adults and children, it simplifies nebulization therapy with a compact design and efficient performance.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEfficient Nebulization Rate\u003c/strong\u003e: Delivers medication at 0.3 ml/min for quick and reliable treatment\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSmall Particle Size (MMAD 3.9µm)\u003c/strong\u003e: Ensures deep penetration into the lower airways for maximum effectiveness\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e12ml Medication Capacity\u003c/strong\u003e: Suitable for a full dose of most prescribed respiratory medications\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eComplete Accessory Kit\u003c/strong\u003e: Includes adult and child masks, mouthpiece, nosepiece, air tube, spare filters, and quick start guide\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eQuiet Operation (\u0026lt;45dB)\u003c/strong\u003e: Offers a comfortable experience, especially for children\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDurable and Lightweight\u003c/strong\u003e: Built to last with a compact form factor for easy handling\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsage\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003ePour the prescribed medication into the nebulizer cup. Connect the air tube and mask or mouthpiece. Turn on the device and inhale the mist slowly and deeply. Use as directed by a healthcare professional. Clean components after each use to maintain hygiene.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy Choose This Product\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eOmron is a globally trusted brand in healthcare technology. The NE-C101 stands out for its simplicity, reliability, and complete kit that supports both pediatric and adult use. It’s ideal for home-based respiratory therapy and ensures consistent results with minimal effort.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eProvides fast relief from respiratory symptoms\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eSuitable for a wide range of conditions including asthma and bronchitis\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eEasy to operate for users of all ages\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eReduces treatment time with efficient medication delivery\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eEnhances comfort with quiet and gentle mist output\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCautions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eUse only under medical supervision\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eClean and disinfect parts after each use to prevent infection\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eDo not use with oil-based medications unless specified\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eKeep away from water and moisture to avoid electrical hazards\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eStore in a cool, dry place and replace filters as recommended\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"68:T515,\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOxygen Mask Child\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eProduct Overview:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eThe Child Oxygen Mask is specially designed to provide effective and comfortable oxygen delivery to pediatric patients. Made from soft, medical-grade materials, it ensures safety and comfort during oxygen therapy for children.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Features:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSoft, hypoallergenic PVC or silicone material gentle on delicate skin\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAdjustable elastic strap for secure and comfortable fit\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTransparent mask for easy monitoring\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLightweight and durable design suitable for pediatric use\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCompatible with standard oxygen tubing\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIndications:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eRecommended for children requiring oxygen therapy due to respiratory illnesses such as asthma, pneumonia, bronchiolitis, or other breathing difficulties.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsage Instructions:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eAttach the oxygen mask to the oxygen supply tubing. Place the mask gently over the child’s nose and mouth, and secure it with the adjustable strap. Ensure the fit is snug but comfortable for optimal oxygen delivery.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStorage:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eKeep in a cool, dry place away from sunlight and contamination.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e69:T455,\u003ch2 class=\"pdp-mod-section-title outer-title\"\u003eProduct details of Getwell Compressor Nebulizer Machine for Child \u0026amp; Adult\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"pdp-product-detail\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"pdp-product-desc\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"html-content pdp-product-highlights\"\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBrand: Getwell (Sister Concern of PRAN-RFL Group)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGetwell Compressor Nebulizer Machine\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e01 Year Brand Warranty.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOne button operation\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEasy carry handle, Easy to clean\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProducts of Getwell Manufactured in China\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWorking Compressor pressure \u0026gt;09 psi, max\u0026gt;25 psi.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCompressor free air flow \u0026gt; 12 L/min.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eElectric requirements- AC 220V/ 50Hz , 0.8A Curent\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSound Level \u0026lt; 55 dB(A)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNebuliser "])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"Rate: 0.4 ml/min (without cap)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMedication Cup Capacity: 8 ml (cc) max.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBox Contents: Compressor Nebulizer, Air Tube, 5 pcs Replacement Filters, Angled Mouthpiece, Adult Mouthpiece, Child Mouthpiece , Instruction Manual.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUsable at Home, Office, Doctor's Chember, Pharmacy, Hospitals \u0026amp; Clinics.\u003cbr\u003eProduct Code-825178\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e6a:T1b2e,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003ch2\u003e\u0026nbsp;Smartcure Mesh Nebuliser Machine Portable - Respiratory Treatment, Handheld, Quiet Operation\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Smartcure Mesh Nebuliser Machine Portable is designed for the effective treatment of respiratory diseases, offering convenience and flexibility with its portable and lightweight design. Utilizing piezoelectric ceramic technology, this nebuliser creates high-speed vibrations that transform medicine into countless micro-atomizing particles, which are then inhaled using masks or mouthpieces.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe device is designed for respiratory disease treatment and the respiratory tract makes piezoelectric ceramic vibrate inharmony that causes high-speed vibration of metal mesh. The medicine liquid will be quickly popped through the micro mesh hole of the mental mesh plate to be countless micro atomizing particles. To the target of inhalation treatment using masks or mouthpieces by importing them into patients' respiratory systems.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA nebulizer is a device that turns liquid medicine into a mist, making it easier to inhale into the lungs. It is used to treat respiratory conditions like asthma, COPD, and other lung issues.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eProduct Key Information\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003ctable style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 95%; border-width: 1px; border-color: #CED4D9;\" border=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cthead\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003eAttribute\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003eDetails\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/thead\u003e\n\u003ctbody\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBrand/Manufacturer Name\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003eSmartcure Limited\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eType\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003eMesh Nebuliser Machine\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTop Features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003eAdjustable Mist Strength, Anti-Dry Design, Lightweight, Dual Power Supply, Quiet Operation\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMedicine Capacity\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003eMax. 8ml\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePower\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003e1.5W\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eParticle Size\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003e\u0026le; 5.0 \u0026micro;m\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNoise Level\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003e\u0026le; 50dB\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSpraying Rate\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003e\u0026ge; 0.2ml/min\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eApplication\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003eRespiratory Treatment\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsed for\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(206, 212, 217); border-width: 1px;\"\u003eTreating Respiratory Diseases\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eFeatures\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDesigned for effective absorption in the throat, trachea, and alveoli.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLightweight and handheld for convenience.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAutomatically shuts off after 10 minutes to prevent damage.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReduces drug residues, ensuring efficient use of medication.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOperates with AA batteries or USB for versatility.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eBenefits\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEffective Respiratory Treatment:\u003c/strong\u003e Designed to treat various respiratory diseases by delivering medicine directly to the respiratory tract.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAdjustable Mist Strength:\u003c/strong\u003e Features 3 working modes to choose the desired mist strength for optimal treatment.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAnti-Dry Design:\u003c/strong\u003e Automatically powers off after 10 minutes to prevent the device from running dry.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLightweight and Portable:\u003c/strong\u003e Easy to carry and use, making it perfect for home or travel.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDual Power Supply:\u003c/strong\u003e Operates with either AA batteries or via USB, providing flexible power options.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eQuiet Operation:\u003c/strong\u003e Functions quietly with a noise level of \u0026le; 50dB, ensuring a peaceful treatment experience.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLarge Medicine Capacity:\u003c/strong\u003e Holds up to 8ml of medicine, reducing the need for frequent refills.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u0026nbsp;How to Use\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePrepare the Nebuliser:\u003c/strong\u003e Ensure the device is clean and filled with the appropriate amount of medicine (up to 8ml).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePower On:\u003c/strong\u003e Choose your power supply option (AA battery or USB) and turn on the device.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSelect Mode:\u003c/strong\u003e Choose one of the 3 mist strength modes as per your requirement.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eInhalation:\u003c/strong\u003e Use the provided mask or mouthpiece to inhale the medication.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAutomatic Power Off:\u003c/strong\u003e The device will automatically shut off after 10 minutes to prevent running dry.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCleaning:\u003c/strong\u003e Follow the instructions for the automatic cleaning function to maintain the nebuliser.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eUses\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNebulizers are used to treat:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAsthma\u003c/strong\u003e: Helps open airways and reduce inflammation.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCOPD\u003c/strong\u003e: Eases symptoms like wheezing and shortness of breath.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCystic Fibrosis\u003c/strong\u003e: Thins mucus for better breathing.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBronchitis\u003c/strong\u003e: Reduces inflammation.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAllergies\u003c/strong\u003e: Delivers medication to reduce lung reactions.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSafety Guide\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBefore using the nebulizer, thoroughly read the user manual provided in the package.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnsure the device and all components are clean and dry before each use.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOnly use medications prescribed or recommended by a healthcare professional.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStore the nebulizer and its components in a cool, dry place. Keep the device out of reach of children.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDo not use the nebulizer if it is damaged or malfunctioning.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAvoid using the device near flammable substances or in high-humidity environments.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIf any irritation or adverse reactions occur during use, discontinue use immediately and seek medical advice.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRegularly inspect the device for wear and tear, and replace any worn parts as necessary.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"6b:T11ed,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eThe Mesh Nebulizer for Adult \u0026amp; Baby offers efficient and quiet atomization of medication, with fine fog particles that can effectively reach different areas of the respiratory tract. Its lightweight design and compatibility with various medical cup sizes make it suitable for both adults and babies.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"font-weight: normal;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eKey features:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e1. Waste Medicine: The nebulizer has a waste medicine capacity of less than or equal to 0.5 ml, ensuring efficient utilisation of the medication.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e2. Flow Rate: The nebulizer has a minimum flow rate of 0.2 ml per minute, enabling effective and timely delivery of medication.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e3. Distribution of Particles: The nebulizer produces atomized particles with a median diameter of approximately 3.7 microns. Approximately 60% of the particles are equal to or smaller than 5 microns, allowing for broad coverage of respiratory conditions in various areas of the respiratory tract, including the high respiratory tract, trachea, bronchial, alveolar, and directly affected areas.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e4. Fitness: The nebulizer is compatible with medical cups ranging from 0.5 ml to 8 ml in capacity, providing flexibility in medication dosage requirements.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e5. Weight: The net weight of the nebulizer is approximately 108 g, making it lightweight and easy to handle.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e6. Noise Level: The nebulizer operates at a noise level of less than or equal to 50 dB(A), ensuring a quiet and comfortable treatment experience.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e7. Dimensions: The nebulizer has approximate dimensions of 67 mm (width) x 48 mm (height) x 107 mm (depth), making it compact and portable.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"6c:T13f2,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003eThe MCP Rubber Hot Water Bag is a must-have for anyone seeking effective heat therapy. Manufactured with high-quality rubber, this water bag is not only durable but also resistant to high water pressure, ensuring a safe and comfortable experience. Whether you're dealing with muscular cramps, joint pain, menstrual discomfort, or backaches, this hot water bag provides soothing warmth to relieve tension and pain.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe bag is leak-proof and easy to clean, making it a practical choice for daily use. Its ability to retain heat for extended periods means you won\u0026rsquo;t need to refill it frequently. The bright, colorful design adds a touch of vibrancy to your pain relief routine, while its ease of use makes it suitable for all ages.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eProduct Key Specifications\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ctable style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; border-color: #7E8C8D;\" border=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cthead\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003eAttribute\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003eDetails\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/thead\u003e\n\u003ctbody\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBrand/Manufacturer\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003eMCP\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAuthorized Seller\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003eGlobal Medical Shop\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMaterial\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003eHigh-quality Rubber\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTop Features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003eLeak-proof, Durable, Long-lasting heat retention\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSize\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003eStandard hot water bag size\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsage\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003eHeat therapy for pain relief\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eApplication Areas\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color: rgb(126, 140, 141);\"\u003eMuscular pain, joint pain, menstrual cramps, stomach aches, back pain\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsage Instructions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFill the bag with hot water (not boiling).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSecure the cap tightly.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eApply to the affected area for heat therapy.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAfter use, empty the water and store it in a dry place.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSafety Guide\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDo not use boiling water to prevent burns.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnsure the cap is tightly sealed to avoid leaks.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStore the bag in a cool, dry place when not in use.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eKeep out of reach of children when filled with hot water.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003cstrong\u003eWhat is a hot water bag used for?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA hot water bag provides warmth and relief from various types of body pain, including muscle aches, cramps, and joint stiffness. It is commonly used to alleviate menstrual pain, sore muscles, and general discomfort caused by colds or flu.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003cstrong\u003eHow long does a hot water bag stay warm?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA hot water bag can typically retain heat for about 1-2 hours, depending on the water temperature and the ambient conditions. Using an insulated cover or wrapping it in a thick towel can help it stay warm longer, which is useful during Bangladesh's chilly winter nights.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat type of water should I use in the hot water bag?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eUse clean, hot tap water that is not boiling (ideally between 40-50\u0026deg;C or 104-122\u0026deg;F). Boiling water can damage the bag material and pose a burn risk.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCan I sleep with a hot water bag?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt\u0026rsquo;s not recommended to sleep with a hot water bag due to the risk of leaks or burns. If you need overnight warmth, consider a heating pad with an auto shut-off function.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow much water should I fill in the hot water bag?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFill the bag about halfway to two-thirds full, leaving room for the air to escape as you secure the cap. This reduces pressure on the seams and minimizes the risk of leakage.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIs it safe to use a hot water bag during pregnancy?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYes, it can be safe for targeted use, such as to relieve back pain or muscle cramps. However, consult with a healthcare provider before use, and avoid prolonged exposure, especially to the abdomen.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eHow often should I replace a hot water bag?\u003c/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eReplace the hot water bag every 1-2 years, or sooner if there are signs of wear, leaks, or damage. Frequent users may need to replace it more often to ensure safe use.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCan children use a hot water bag?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYes, but with caution. Always supervise children and wrap the hot water bag in a cloth to prevent burns.\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"6d:Tb62,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003ch2\u003eProduct details of Hot Water Bag 2 Litter (12*7 Inches)\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMade OF natural rubber.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eImported from China.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRetains heat for an extra long time.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRibbed outer surface helps maintain liquid temperature.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHot water bottle can be used alone as a remedy for aches, pains and sports injuries.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIn addition to the traditional hot therapy, it can also double up as a cold compress for kids with fever or to reduce swelling for minor injuries.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSize : 12''(32cm) x 7''(19.4cm).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHeavy Duty Hot Water Bottle Bag.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDurable and Long-lasting.Ribbed Outer Surface for Safer Skin Contact and Longer Heat Retaining.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePackage includes one 2L hot water Beg.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNotice,because of the natural rubber material,there may be some odor on their first use,you can put it in water for hours to remove odors;we recommend not to touch skin directly after hot water is injected to avoid scalding,use it safely with suitable temperature.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color:rgb(17,17,17);\"\u003eEXCEPTIONALLY HIGH 56% RUBBER CONTENT far outperforms other hot water bottles that use chalk fillers or are made with vinyl and PVC. This hot water bottle is the real deal with genuine grade A natural rubber which means hot water stays hot longer. Also works as an excellent cold pack to reduce swelling and other maladies. We do not provide rubber hot water bottles which have a lower rubber content and are bulked out with chalk and other chemical fillers. These types of bottles are ineffective at retaining heat and wear out much quicker leading to leaking and bursting. This hot water bottle has a higher rubber content (56%) which has greater heat retention. That's why they're a little bit more pricey - but we've chosen a bottle that, with the right care and use will work safely for a longer period of time. NON-TOXIC (BPA \u0026amp; PHTHALATE FREE) MATERIALS designed in accordance with American health standards. This rubber hot water bottle is Eco-Friendly and UL Tested for safety and reliability. These divine Hot Water Bottles are covered in super soft, faux fur and each contains a real rubber water bottle. What could be more comfortable than snuggling up with this high quality, smooth hot water bottle on a chilly night?. If the smell of rubber bothers you, please be considerate of your purchase. At PETERPAN we understand that some consumers can find the smell of this product overpowering on initial use, this is because filling a bottle with heated water amplifies the smell and this can be unpleasant for some. Before use, fill the bottle with hot water. In well-ventilated area, allow the water in the bag to cool completely.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn2.arogga.com/eyJidWNrZXQiOiJhcm9nZ2EiLCJrZXkiOiJtZWRpY2luZURlc2NyaXB0aW9uXC8zN1wvMzc1MjEtMDB5a2NmYmhlaTltei5qcGVnIiwiZWRpdHMiOltdfQ==\" alt=\"f768e982fea693bb35f9cec67507a950.jpg\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"6e:Tb07,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHot and Cold Compress Gel Heat Pad Ice Bag\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe \u003cstrong\u003eHot and Cold Compress Gel Heat Pad Ice Bag\u003c/strong\u003e is a versatile and reusable product designed to provide targeted pain relief. Whether you need heat therapy for muscle relaxation or cold therapy to reduce swelling and inflammation, this gel pad is a convenient and effective solution for various aches and injuries.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003chr /\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Features:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDual Functionality\u003c/strong\u003e: Can be used for both hot and cold compress applications.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eReusable Design\u003c/strong\u003e: Durable, leak-proof, and reusable for long-term use.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFlexible Gel\u003c/strong\u003e: Retains flexibility even when frozen, allowing it to conform to any body part.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSafe and Non-Toxic\u003c/strong\u003e: Made with skin-safe and non-toxic materials.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCompact and Portable\u003c/strong\u003e: Lightweight and easy to carry, suitable for home or travel use.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003chr /\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUses and Benefits:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCold Therapy\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReduces swelling and inflammation.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProvides relief from headaches, sprains, bruises, and minor burns.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIdeal for post-surgery or injury recovery.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHeat Therapy\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEases muscle stiffness and tension.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRelieves chronic pain such as arthritis or backaches.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePromotes better blood circulation.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003chr /\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor Cold Therapy\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePlace the gel pad in the freezer for at least 2 hours.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWrap it in a cloth or towel before applying to the affected area.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor Heat Therapy\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePlace the gel pad in a microwave for 20-30 seconds (time may vary).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTest the temperature to ensure it's not too hot.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWrap it in a towel and apply it to the target area.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003chr /\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePrecautions:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDo not apply directly to the skin to avoid burns or frostbite.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDo not overheat in the microwave.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eKeep away from sharp objects to prevent punctures.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNot suitable for ingestion or use on open wounds.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003chr /\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eProduct Specifications:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMaterial\u003c/strong\u003e: Non-toxic gel with a flexible outer covering.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSize\u003c/strong\u003e: Compact and ergonomic design for easy handling.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eColor\u003c/strong\u003e: Typically available in blue or transparent gel bags.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003chr /\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe \u003cstrong\u003eHot and Cold Compress Gel Heat Pad Ice Bag\u003c/strong\u003e is an essential tool for managing everyday pain and injuries, making it a must-have in your first-aid kit or wellness routine.\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"6f:T76f,\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"\u003eCode:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eB 02\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"\u003eSizes Available:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eS, M, L, XL\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"ql-align-justify\"\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"\u003eCervical Collar soft with support\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eis used for supporting, immobilizing or adjusting the neck in the required position. Recommended where a partial or controlled immobilization of the cervical region is required.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"ql-align-justify\"\u003eAnatomical shape\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"ql-align-justify\"\u003eWell ventilated\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"ql-align-justify\"\u003eHigh density PU foam\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"ql-align-justify\"\u003eSkin matching color\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"ql-align-justify\"\u003eHypo allergenic\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"ql-align-justify\"\u003eMade from high density PU foam 30 kg/m3 witch provide better support and enhanced immobilization. It has higher cushioning, better comfort, higher patient compliance and ling functional life.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"ql-align-justify\"\u003eReinforced with LDPE sheet with thick round edgesto enhance immobilization. Edge doesn\u0026rsquo;t bite into the skin, so is more comfortable. Edge doesn\u0026rsquo;t not bite into the foam, enhances life of the collar.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"ql-align-justify\"\u003eRust proof, Poly propylene eyelets provide proper ventilation and enhanced paitent comfort.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"ql-align-justify\"\u003eDermophillic cotton stockinet with high GSM is trated to improve hypoallergenicity, ensureno rush or allergy. Improves comfort and improves overall life of the collar.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"ql-align-center\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSize Chart\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn2.arogga.com/eyJidWNrZXQiOiJhcm9nZ2EiLCJrZXkiOiJtZWRpY2luZURlc2NyaXB0aW9uXC8zNlwvMzYyODgtMHJvZzJtc3poOWo5OS5wbmciLCJlZGl0cyI6W119\" alt=\"eyJidWNrZXQiOiJhcm9nZ2EiLCJrZXkiOiJtZWRpY2luZURlc2NyaXB0aW9uXC8zNlwvMzYyODgtMHJvZzJtc3poOWo5OS5wbmciLCJlZGl0cyI6W119\" width=\"563\" height=\"188\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e70:T80f,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003eThe \u003cstrong\u003eCervical Pillow Regular (G-201)\u003c/strong\u003e is specially designed to provide optimal support and comfort for the neck and shoulders. It is ideal for individuals experiencing neck pain, stiffness, or discomfort, offering a therapeutic solution for better posture and improved sleep quality.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003chr /\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eProduct Highlights:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eErgonomic Design:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCrafted to support the natural curve of the cervical spine, promoting proper alignment during sleep.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMaterial:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMade from high-quality, soft, and durable materials that ensure comfort and longevity.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTherapeutic Benefits:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRelieves neck pain and stiffness by maintaining a neutral position for the cervical spine.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReduces strain on neck muscles and ligaments during rest.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUniversal Fit:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDesigned for regular use, suitable for all sleeping positions, including back and side sleepers.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLightweight and Portable:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEasy to carry, making it perfect for use at home or during travel.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003chr /\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Benefits:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHelps alleviate cervical discomfort and improves posture.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnhances sleep quality by reducing neck strain.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSupports rehabilitation for individuals with cervical spondylosis or related conditions.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003chr /\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsage Instructions:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePlace the cervical pillow on your bed with the curved side under your neck.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnsure that your head and neck are comfortably supported while lying down.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse regularly for best results in relieving neck discomfort.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003chr /\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCare Instructions:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClean the pillow cover as per the manufacturer’s instructions.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAvoid washing the pillow core unless specified to preserve its structure and durability.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"71:T8e1,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003ch1\u003eProduct Details of RBC Compressor Nebulizer\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eFeatures\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Latex free\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Easy to clean\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Ideal for all ages\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Easy carry handle\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Two storage compartments\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Complete Nebulizer kit included\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eTechnical Data:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Liter Flow Range: \u0026gt;6.7 L/min\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Average Nebulization Rate \u0026gt; 0.25mL/min\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Sound Level: \u0026lt;65dB(A)\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Particle Size: 0.5-10 um\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Operation Humidity Range: 15 to 80% RH\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Operating Pressure Range: 9.5\u0026ndash;19psi\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Compressor Pressure Range: 22-58 psi\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Product size: 300*180*110mm\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Unit weight: 1.5kg\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\"\u003e\u0026middot;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Use Life: 3 Years\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"72:T72a,\u003cdiv class=\"product-tabs-wrapper\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"container\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"row\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"col-12 poduct-tabs-inner\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"woocommerce-tabs wc-tabs-wrapper tabs-layout-tabs\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"wd-accordion-item\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--description wd-active panel wc-tab\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"wc-tab-inner\"\u003e\n\u003ch1\u003ePromixco Compressor Nebulizer\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eDescription\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePromixco Pro\u0026nbsp; is a priced inhaler that assists in the treatment of upper and lower respiratory disorders such as colds or asthma. The model utilizes advanced compressor-compressed air technology to aerosolize the active ingredients. This finest nebulization achieves particularly high efficiency. It still works in a nice place, with a volume of 55 decibels. Nebulisation with compressed air technology\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHighly efficient due to very precise nebulization\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEspecially successful via high breathability\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFull range of accessories: mask, mouthpiece or nasal adapter inhalation\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003esuitable for children\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExtra-long tube \u0026ndash; 2 m\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe certified medical device according to Medical Device Directive\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTargeted treatment of upper and lower respiratory tract disorders (e.g., asthma).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg class=\"wp-image-14519 aligncenter\" src=\"https://cdn2.arogga.com/eyJidWNrZXQiOiJhcm9nZ2EiLCJrZXkiOiJtZWRpY2luZURlc2NyaXB0aW9uXC80MFwvNDA0NDEtMGduYWJ5cnlhc2VsaS5qcGVnIiwiZWRpdHMiOltdfQ==\" alt=\"\" width=\"283\" height=\"376\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"wd-accordion-item\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"wd-accordion-item\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"wd-accordion-item\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"wd-accordion-item\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"container related-and-upsells\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"related-products\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e73:T14e5,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eThe United Medicare Grey Regular Cervical Pillow (B-05) is designed to provide therapeutic assistance and support for the neck while promoting restful and comfortable sleep. It is specifically designed to reduce snoring and apnea, relieve neck pain, and promote optimal spinal alignment.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"font-weight: normal;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eProduct Details:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eBrand: United Medicare\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eModel Name: Cervical Pillow\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eCountry of Origin: India\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eProduct Code: B-05\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eFeatures:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e1. Contoured Design: The cervical pillow features a distinctive design with different heights on two sides. This contoured shape provides therapeutic support to the neck muscles and ligaments, allowing them to sleep in a healthy position.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e2. Firmness and Resilience: The pillow offers a balance of firmness and resilience to provide optimal support and comfort.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e3. Softness and Comfort: Despite its therapeutic design, the pillow is also designed to provide softness and comfort, ensuring a restful sleep experience.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e4. Optimal Spinal Alignment: The contoured design of the pillow helps maintain optimal spinal alignment, which is beneficial for both back and side sleepers. It supports the natural curvature of the neck and spine.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e5. Healing Benefits: The United Medicare Grey Regular Cervical Pillow can be particularly helpful in various circumstances, including early rheumatoid disease, geriatric care, stiff cervical spondylitis, and cervical disc disease. It can aid in promoting comfort and alleviating symptoms associated with these conditions.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"74:T1512,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eThe United Medicare Grey Contoured Cervical Pillow (B-06) is designed to provide therapeutic assistance and support for the neck while promoting restful and comfortable sleep. It is specifically designed to reduce snoring and apnea, relieve neck pain, and promote optimal spinal alignment.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: normal;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eProduct Details:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eBrand: United Medicare\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eModel Name: Cervical Pillow\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eCountry of Origin: India\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eProduct Code: B-06\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"font-weight: normal;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003eFeatures:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e1. Contoured Design: The cervical pillow features a distinctive design with different heights on two sides. This contoured shape provides therapeutic support to the neck muscles and ligaments, allowing them to sleep in a healthy position.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e2. Firmness and Resilience: The pillow offers a balance of firmness and resilience to provide optimal support and comfort\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e3. Softness and Comfort: Despite its therapeutic design, the pillow is also designed to provide softness and comfort, ensuring a restful sleep experience.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e4. Optimal Spinal Alignment: The contoured design of the pillow helps maintain optimal spinal alignment, which is beneficial for both back and side sleepers. It supports the natural curvature of the neck and spine.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"\u003e5. Healing Benefits: The United Medicare Grey Contoured Cervical Pillow can be particularly helpful in various circumstances, including early rheumatoid disease, geriatric care, stiff cervical spondylitis, and cervical disc disease. It can aid in promoting comfort and alleviating symptoms associated with these conditions.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"75:T553,\u003ch2 class=\"default\"\u003eProduct description\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"productDescription\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-small\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTynor Cervical Orthosis (Philadelphia) Plastazote is an advanced collar with a scientific design which ensures perfect immobilization and comfort. The frontal opening allows the use of tracheotomy tube and improves ventilation. Designed with swollen balloon shape makes it an ideal collar for treating burn patients. Also used in cervical disc disease, post-operative care, post-traction stabilization, fractures of the cervical spine, extrication, and transportation of the accident victims. \"Plastazote\" is durable, non-allergenic, light in weight, \u0026amp; easy to clean. The frontal and the rear splints are anatomically designed to support the neck, limit the flexion and extension movement of the cervical spine. Pre-moulded chin and the balloon design gives only a rim contact to the body without involving the neck surface. Two piece designs with an inbuilt chin rest also help in better immobilization. Use this product under the strict guidance of a qualified doctor. Discontinue use and seek the guidance of a qualified doctor, in case allergy, rash or itching. Some wash care instructions are hand wash with mild detergent and water, do not dry clean, iron and bleach. Available in five sizes children, small, medium, large and XL.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e76:Td85,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003ch2\u003eProduct details of Woodwards Gripe Water - 130ml (Indian)\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWoodward's Gripe Water is an Ayurvedic remedy designed to gently relieve digestive discomforts like colic, gas, and acidity in infants. Formulated with key ingredients such as Dill Seed Oil and Sarjikakshara, this trusted gripe water neutralizes stomach acids and supports healthy digestion, particularly during teething. Free from alcohol and harsh chemicals, it is safe for regular use, helping your baby stay comfortable and cheerful. The convenient packaging makes it easy to carry when traveling with your baby.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eProduct Benefits\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUseful during the teething period\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003epromotes and aids digestion\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnsure healthy growth\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not contain alcohol\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003econtains oil of dil herd and sarjikakshar\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003econvenient pack that you can carry whenever you travel\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWoodward's Gripe Water is an Ayurvedic formulation with a combination of Dill oil and Sarjikakshara that provides symptomatic relief – from stomach pain caused due to gas, acidity and indigestion in infants and children. It is safe – strict checks are done at every stage of the manufacturing process to ensure the quality and hygiene of the product. Generations of mothers have trusted Woodward's to provide Colic remedies to their crying babies.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eProduct Key Specifications \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003ctable style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;border-spacing:10px;border-color:#7E8C8D;\" border=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cthead\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003eAttribute\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003eDetails\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/thead\u003e\n\u003ctbody\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBrand/Manufacturer\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003eWoodward's\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eType\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003eGripe Water\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTop Features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003eAlcohol-free, Ayurvedic, Colic and Gas Relief\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSize\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003e130ml\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCount\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003e1 Bottle\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsed For\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003eColic, Gas, Indigestion in Infants\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Ingredients\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"border-color:rgb(126,140,141);\"\u003eDill Seed Oil, Sarjikakshara\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDill Seed Oil (Terpeneless)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSarjikakshara (Sodium Hydrogen Carbonate)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSodium Benzoate\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSodium Propylparaben\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSodium Methylparaben\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBronopo\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAdminister Woodward's Gripe Water as per the dosage instructions on the bottle or as directed by your pediatrician. For best results, it is usually given during or after meals.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSafety Guide\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAlways follow the recommended dosage.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place, away from sunlight.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eKeep out of the reach of children.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"77:Tec2,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eMamaearth Milky Soft Face Cream is a gentle, nourishing moisturizer specially formulated for the delicate skin of babies. Enriched with natural ingredients like milk protein, murumuru butter, oat oil, and lavender, this cream helps soothe dryness, protect against irritation, and maintain a healthy skin barrier. With a pH-balanced formula and dermatologically tested safety, it’s a trusted choice for daily baby skincare.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNet Weight\u003c/strong\u003e: 60g\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eActive Ingredients\u003c/strong\u003e: Milk protein, murumuru butter, oat oil, oat flour, lavender oil\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003epH-Balanced Formula\u003c/strong\u003e: Maintains the natural balance of baby’s sensitive skin\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDermatologically Tested\u003c/strong\u003e: Safe for daily use on newborns and infants\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNo Harmful Chemicals\u003c/strong\u003e: Free from parabens, sulfates, mineral oil, PEGs, phthalates, and artificial fragrances\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMoisturizing and Protective\u003c/strong\u003e: Locks in moisture and forms a protective barrier against dryness\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMade in India\u003c/strong\u003e: Manufactured with high safety and quality standards\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsage Instructions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eTake a small amount of cream on your palm. Apply gently over your baby’s face and neck. Massage in upward circular motions until fully absorbed. Use twice daily or as needed to keep skin soft and hydrated. Store in a cool, dry place and keep the cap tightly closed after use.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDeep Hydration\u003c/strong\u003e: Murumuru butter and milk protein help retain moisture and prevent dryness\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSoothes Irritated Skin\u003c/strong\u003e: Oat oil and lavender oil calm itchy or chapped areas\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStrengthens Skin Barrier\u003c/strong\u003e: Helps protect against environmental stressors and allergens\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGentle and Non-Greasy\u003c/strong\u003e: Absorbs quickly without leaving a sticky residue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIdeal for Sensitive Skin\u003c/strong\u003e: Mild formulation suitable for daily use from birth\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCautions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eFor external use only\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eAvoid contact with eyes; rinse immediately if contact occurs\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eDiscontinue use if irritation or redness develops\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eKeep out of reach of children when not in use\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eAlways perform a patch test before first use\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy Choose This Product\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eMamaearth Milky Soft Face Cream offers a perfect blend of nature and science to care for your baby’s skin. Its nourishing ingredients and toxin-free formulation make it a safe and effective choice for parents who want gentle, long-lasting hydration without compromise. Whether your baby has dry, sensitive, or normal skin, this cream provides comfort, protection, and peace of mind with every application.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"78:T15d2,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cdiv class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+\u0026amp;]:mt-5\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\"\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAveeno Baby Calming Comfort Lotion with Prebiotic Oat \u0026amp; Lavender Scent (227g)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eThe Aveeno Baby Calming Comfort Lotion is a gentle and nourishing moisturizer designed for a baby's delicate skin. Infused with the soothing scent of lavender and chamomile, this lotion helps relax and calm your baby while providing long-lasting hydration. Its dermatologist-tested formula includes prebiotic oat to nurture the skin’s natural moisture barrier.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Features\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePrebiotic Oat Formula\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eSupports the skin’s natural moisture barrier while providing nourishment and protection.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLavender and Chamomile Scent\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eDesigned to calm and soothe, making it perfect for bedtime routines.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eClinically Proven Gentle\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eFree of parabens, phthalates, and dyes, making it safe for a baby's sensitive skin.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e24-Hour Moisturization\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eProvides long-lasting hydration to keep the skin soft and smooth.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNon-Greasy and Quick Absorbing\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eLeaves skin feeling refreshed and comfortable without any sticky residue.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eTake a small amount of the lotion into your hands.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eGently massage it onto your baby’s skin, focusing on dry areas.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eUse after bath time or as needed, especially before bedtime to help relax your baby.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Ingredients\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePrebiotic Oat\u003c/strong\u003e: Nourishes the skin and reinforces its natural moisture barrier.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGlycerin\u003c/strong\u003e: Hydrates and locks in moisture.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLavender and Chamomile\u003c/strong\u003e: Provide calming and soothing benefits.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eSoothes and moisturizes baby’s delicate skin.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eHelps promote a sense of relaxation with its calming lavender scent.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eHypoallergenic and gentle for sensitive skin.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003ePerfect for daily use or as part of a bedtime routine.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIdeal For\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eBabies with normal, dry, or sensitive skin.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eUse after baths or during massages to create a calming experience.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eParents seeking a gentle lotion with soothing properties for bedtime routines.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eWith Aveeno Baby Calming Comfort Lotion, you can create a soothing and hydrating experience that helps your baby feel calm, relaxed, and comforted.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003ePackaging can be changed due to different editions\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMade in USA\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"79:Tdb5,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003ePampers Baby Dry Size 7 Nappy Pants are designed to provide up to 12 hours of leak-free protection for active toddlers weighing 15kg and above. With a flexible waistband and soft materials, these pants-style diapers offer a comfortable fit that adapts to your child’s movements. The Jumbo+Pack includes 58 nappies, making it a convenient and cost-effective choice for busy parents.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUp to 12 Hours of Dryness:\u003c/strong\u003e Extra dry layer absorbs wetness quickly to keep baby dry overnight\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e360° Comfort Fit:\u003c/strong\u003e Stretchy waistband and leg cuffs adapt to baby’s shape for a secure fit\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAir Channels:\u003c/strong\u003e Promote breathability to keep skin fresh and reduce irritation\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEasy Tear Sides:\u003c/strong\u003e Simplifies changing by allowing quick removal\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDermatologically Tested:\u003c/strong\u003e Gentle on sensitive skin and free from EU perfume allergens\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLeak Protection:\u003c/strong\u003e Safety leg cuffs help prevent leaks around the legs\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLatex-Free and FSC-Certified Materials:\u003c/strong\u003e Made with responsibly sourced materials for added safety and sustainability\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsage\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003ePull up the nappy pants like regular underwear. Ensure the waistband is snug but comfortable. After use, tear the sides for easy removal and dispose of the nappy in a waste bin. Do not flush. Ideal for daytime and overnight use.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy Choose This Product\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003ePampers is a globally trusted brand known for its commitment to baby comfort and hygiene. These Size 7 nappy pants are tailored for toddlers who need reliable protection and freedom of movement. With advanced absorbency and breathable design, they offer peace of mind for parents and uninterrupted play or sleep for children.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eKeeps baby dry and comfortable for extended periods\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eSupports active toddlers with flexible, secure fit\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eReduces risk of skin irritation and rashes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eConvenient for quick changes, especially during travel or outings\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eOffers excellent value with 58 nappies in a single pack\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCautions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eFor external use only\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eChange nappies regularly to maintain hygiene and prevent discomfort\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eStore in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eKeep packaging materials out of reach of children to avoid suffocation risk\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eDo not flush used nappies; dispose of them responsibly\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"7a:T573,\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTwinkle Baby Soap 75g – Buy 2 Get 1 Free Offer\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTwinkle Baby Soap is specially formulated to care for your little one’s delicate skin. Enriched with nourishing ingredients like Vitamin E, Cocoa Butter, and Milk Protein, this soap gently cleanses while keeping the skin soft, hydrated, and protected. Its antibacterial formula helps guard against germs, making it a trusted choice for daily use.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eProduct Highlights\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWeight\u003c/strong\u003e: 75g per bar\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOffer\u003c/strong\u003e: Buy 2 bars, get 1 free\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Ingredients\u003c/strong\u003e:\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVitamin E\u003c/strong\u003e – Moisturizes and protects\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCocoa Butter\u003c/strong\u003e – Softens and smooths skin\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMilk Protein\u003c/strong\u003e – Nourishes and maintains moisture\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSkin Type\u003c/strong\u003e: Suitable for all skin types, especially sensitive baby skin\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n