\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eBelt System\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eSize\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eSmall (Up to 8kg)\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eCount\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e44 Pcs\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eTop Features\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eWetness Indicator, Cottony Soft, Leak proof.\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eApplication\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eDisposable diaper for infants\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eUsed for\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003eProviding comfort and protection for babies weighing up to 8 kg\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"summary\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSavlon Twinkle Baby Diaper Benefits\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e✔ Keeps your baby dry, reducing the frequency of diaper changes.\u003cbr /\u003e✔ Gentle on sensitive skin, minimizing the risk of rashes.\u003cbr /\u003e✔ Adjustable belt ensures the diaper stays in place, providing leak protection.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e \u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"summary\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eSoft non-woven fabric\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eFluff pulp and super absorbent polymer\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eBreathable polyethylene film\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eAdjustable belt with adhesive tabs\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"summary\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003ePreparation: Lay your baby on a clean, flat surface.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003ePositioning: Place the diaper under your baby with the adhesive tabs at the back.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eSecuring: Pull the adjustable belt over your baby's waist and fasten the adhesive tabs securely, ensuring a snug fit around the legs and waist.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eDisposal: After use, roll the diaper into a tight ball, secure it with the adhesive tabs, and dispose of it in a designated waste bin.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"summary\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSafety Guide\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eFor external use only.\u003cbr /\u003eKeep out of reach of children to prevent accidental suffocation.\u003cbr /\u003eChange the diaper promptly when soiled to maintain hygiene and prevent skin irritation.\u003cbr /\u003eDiscontinue use if any signs of allergic reaction or irritation occur, and consult a pediatrician if necessary.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\"\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"7c:T12d4,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eMum Mum Baby Pant Diapers in size S are specially designed for newborns and infants weighing between 4 to 8 kilograms. With a soft, pant-style fit and advanced absorbency features, these diapers offer gentle protection and comfort for your baby’s sensitive skin. Whether it’s nap time, playtime, or overnight sleep, this diaper ensures dryness and ease of movement.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePant-Style Design\u003c/strong\u003e: Easy to wear and remove, ideal for babies who are starting to move\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSoft \u0026amp; Gentle Texture\u003c/strong\u003e: Mimics the feel of a mother’s touch for added comfort\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSuperior Absorbency\u003c/strong\u003e: Keeps baby dry for extended periods\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBreathable Layers\u003c/strong\u003e: Allows airflow to prevent moisture buildup and skin irritation\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLeak-Proof Construction\u003c/strong\u003e: Secure fit helps prevent leaks and messes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWetness Indicator\u003c/strong\u003e: Changes color to signal when it’s time for a diaper change\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUV Sterilized\u003c/strong\u003e: Enhances hygiene by reducing microbial exposure\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e360° Elastic Waistband\u003c/strong\u003e: Provides a snug yet flexible fit that adapts to baby’s movements\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePack Size Options\u003c/strong\u003e: Available in convenient packs, including 40 pieces for long-term use\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsage\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eGently pull the diaper up like underwear, ensuring the waistband sits comfortably around the waist. Adjust the leg cuffs to prevent leaks. Change the diaper every 4–6 hours or when the wetness indicator shows saturation. Dispose of used diapers in a waste bin.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy Choose This Product\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eMum Mum Baby Pant Diapers offer a thoughtful balance of comfort, protection, and practicality. Their pant-style design supports active movement, while the breathable and leak-proof features ensure your baby stays dry and happy. The UV sterilization process adds an extra layer of safety, making them a dependable choice for everyday use.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eKeeps baby dry and comfortable throughout the day and night\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eReduces risk of diaper rash and skin irritation\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eSupports active movement without discomfort\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eEncourages independence in older infants\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eConvenient for travel, daycare, and home use\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCautions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eFor single use only; do not reuse\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eStore in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eDo not flush; dispose of responsibly\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eMonitor for signs of skin sensitivity and discontinue use if irritation occurs\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003eKeep out of reach of children when not in use\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"7d:Tcb0,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eMum Mum Baby Pant Diapers are designed to offer reliable protection and comfort for active babies weighing between 12 to 17 kilograms. With a pant-style design and advanced absorbency features, these diapers make diapering easier for parents while keeping babies dry and happy throughout the day and night.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePant-Style Design\u003c/strong\u003e: Easy to wear and remove, ideal for toddlers who are starting to move independently\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBreathable Layers\u003c/strong\u003e: Promotes airflow to prevent heat buildup and reduce the risk of rashes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLeakage-Proof Construction\u003c/strong\u003e: Keeps moisture locked in for longer periods, ensuring uninterrupted sleep and play\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWetness Indicator\u003c/strong\u003e: Changes color to signal when it’s time for a diaper change\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e360-Degree Elastic Waistband\u003c/strong\u003e: Provides a snug yet flexible fit for active movement\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePack of 4\u003c/strong\u003e: Convenient for short trips or trial use\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUsage\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eGently pull the diaper up like underwear, ensuring the waistband sits comfortably around the waist. Adjust the leg cuffs to prevent leaks. Change the diaper when the wetness indicator signals or every 4–6 hours. Dispose of used diapers responsibly.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy Choose This Product\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eMum Mum Baby Pant Diapers combine comfort, safety, and practicality in one compact pack. Their pant-style fit makes them ideal for babies who are crawling, walking, or transitioning to toilet training. The breathable and leak-proof design ensures your baby stays dry and comfortable, while the UV sterilization adds an extra layer of hygiene.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eSupports active movement without discomfort\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eHelps prevent diaper rash and skin irritation\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eReduces the frequency of leaks and clothing changes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eEncourages independence in older babies\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eConvenient for travel or daycare use\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eCaut\u003cstrong\u003ei\u003c/strong\u003eons\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eFor single use only; do not reuse\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eStore in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eDo not flush; dispose of in a waste bin\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eMonitor for signs of skin irritation and discontinue use if necessary\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;\"\u003eKeep out of reach of children when not in use\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"7e:T59b,\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eParachute Just For Baby - Milky Glow Saffron \u0026amp; Milk Soap 75g\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"\u003e• Brand: Parachute Just For Baby\u003cbr /\u003e• Product Type: Baby Soap\u003cbr /\u003e• Variant: Milky Glow\u003cbr /\u003e• 100% Safe Ingredients\u003cbr /\u003e• Gives baby healthy glow from within\u003cbr /\u003e• Enriched with Saffron and Milk\u003cbr /\u003e• Gently cleanses delicate skinParachute Just for Baby Milky Glow Baby Soap gently cleanses your baby’s delicate skin, giving it healthy glow from within. With 100% safe ingredients, an allergy-tested \u0026amp; paraben-free formula, Parachute Just For Baby Milky Glow Baby Soap nourishes your baby's skin and gives your baby a healthy glow. To use the baby soap on your little angel – Lather on your hands and then gently apply on your baby’s body. Rinse off with lukewarm water. Follow with Parachute Just For Baby Milky Glow Lotion for best results. Parachute Just for Baby Milky Glow Baby Soap is for external use only. In case of irritation, rinse off and discontinue use. Keep away from heat, direct sunlight, \u0026amp; reach of children. Store in a cool \u0026amp; dry place away from sunlight. The Parachute Just for Baby care range is enriched with Paraben Free ingredients, 100% natural moisturizers and is Australian Allergy Certified and MadeSafe Certified. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"5:[[\"$\",\"$L27\",\"0\",{\"data\":{\"block\":\"Web Home Top Carousel\",\"block_subtitle\":\"\",\"block_machine_name\":\"web_home_top_carousel\",\"block_type\":\"carousel\",\"block_id\":113,\"block_styles\":\"\",\"block_color_code\":\"\",\"block_weight\":1,\"block_display_type\":\"web_top_carousel\",\"block_view_all_link\":\"\",\"block_start_date\":\"2025-10-05 11:17:00\",\"block_end_date\":\"2027-11-22 18:00:00\",\"block_page_banner\":[],\"block_link_parameter\":\"\",\"block_per_page\":10,\"block_infinity\":0,\"block_data\":[{\"title\":\"১ নম্বর প্ল্যাটফর্ম\",\"subtitle\":\"\",\"is_external\":0,\"color_code\":\"\",\"is_category_home\":\"\",\"button_title\":\"\",\"alt\":\"১ নম্বর প্ল্যাটফর্ম\",\"link\":\"category\",\"route\":\"\",\"link_parameter\":{\"id\":\"6322\",\"tax_category\":\"medicine\",\"_order\":\"pv_allow_sales:desc\"},\"width\":\"\",\"height\":\"\",\"uuid\":\"67f39647e4c5d\",\"file\":[{\"title\":\"১ নম্বর প্ল্যাটফর্ম Web Banner.png\",\"src\":\"https://cdn2.arogga.com/eyJidWNrZXQiOiJhcm9nZ2EiLCJrZXkiOiJCbG9jay1iX2NvbmZpZ1wvMFwvMTEzLVdlYi1CYW5uZXItdXI5MHd5LnBuZyIsImVkaXRzIjpbXX0=\"}],\"file_banner\":[]},{\"title\":\"Skin'O\",\"subtitle\":\"\",\"is_external\":0,\"color_code\":\"\",\"is_category_home\":\"\",\"button_title\":\"\",\"alt\":\"Skin'O\",\"link\":\"brand\",\"route\":\"public\",\"link_parameter\":{\"id\":\"102037\"},\"width\":\"\",\"height\":\"\",\"uuid\":\"68c2cef1af188\",\"file\":[{\"title\":\"arogga Web Banner Update.png\",\"src\":\"https://cdn2.arogga.com/eyJidWNrZXQiOiJhcm9nZ2EiLCJrZXkiOiJCbG9jay1iX2NvbmZpZ1wvMFwvMTEzLWFyb2dnYS1XZWItQmFubmVyLVVwZGF0ZS12bXhpdGEucG5